headline: UDR's Q4 FFOA Beats Estimates, Revenues & Same-Store NOI Grow Y/Y
summary: UDR posts Q4 FFOA of 64 cents, matching estimates, as higher occupancy lifts same-store NOI despite softer lease rates and a slight revenue miss.

headline: 36 U.S. REITs Expected To Raise Dividends In Q1 2026
summary: 36 publicly traded US REITs are projected to increase dividend payouts in the first quarter, according to S&P Global Market Intelligence forecasts.
